## 📧 Prompt 1 — Professional Email

### 🎯 Objective

Write a professional business email with a clear structure.

#### Prompt

```text
Act as an experienced business communication specialist.

Write a professional email.

Purpose:
[Describe]

Audience:
[Recipient]

Tone:
Professional, concise, and polite.

Include:

• Subject suggestion
• Greeting
• Clear introduction
• Main message
• Call to action
• Professional closing

Format the email professionally.
```

#### Example Use Cases

- Job Application
- Follow-up Email
- Client Communication
- Meeting Request
- Project Update

