## ✍️ Prompt 2 — Blog Article

### 🎯 Objective

Generate a well-structured blog article.

#### Prompt

```text
Act as a professional content writer.

Write a detailed blog article.

Topic:
[Insert Topic]

Target Audience:
[Audience]

Length:
1000–1500 words

Writing Style:
Educational and engaging.

Include:

• Title
• Introduction
• Main Sections
• Practical Examples
• Key Takeaways
• Conclusion

Use headings, bullet points, and short paragraphs.
```

#### Example Topics

- Artificial Intelligence
- Prompt Engineering
- Remote Jobs
- Data Annotation
- Machine Learning

