## 📚 Prompt 3 — Technical Documentation

### 🎯 Objective

Create clean and professional documentation.

#### Prompt

```text
Act as a senior technical writer.

Write technical documentation for:

Project:
[Project Name]

Audience:
Developers and end users.

Include:

• Project Overview
• Features
• Prerequisites
• Installation
• Usage Guide
• Folder Structure
• Examples
• Best Practices
• Troubleshooting
• FAQ

Write using Markdown formatting.
```

### Best For

- GitHub Projects
- APIs
- AI Projects
- Software Documentation
- Internal Guides

